1. *Savet* nam je da provedemo više vremena u prirodi. (The advice was for us to spend more time in nature.)

2. Dobili smo *savet* od stručnjaka. (We got advice from an expert.)

3. Nije nam dao nikakav *savet*. (He didn't give us any advice.)

4. Ona je dala *savet* svom sinu. (She gave advice to her son.)

5. Nismo poslušali *savet*. (We didn't follow the advice.)

6. Slobodno mi možete dati *savet*. (Feel free to give me advice.)